short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Converts week number and year to month and month number based on input.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension converts a given week number into the corresponding month for any year between 1950 and 2030. It provides users with an efficient and quick way to determine the month for a specified week within the defined date range
